                <div class="action-row"><span class="row-icon">↻</span><span class="row-copy"><strong>Reload</strong><span>Refresh this transcript.</span></span></div>
                <div class="action-row"><span class="row-icon">＋</span><span class="row-copy"><strong>New session</strong><span>Start beside this directory.</span></span></div>
                <div class="action-row"><span class="row-icon">›_</span><span class="row-copy"><strong>Open terminal</strong><span>Open a shell for this workspace.</span></span></div>
                <div class="action-row"><span class="row-icon">⤳</span><span class="row-copy"><strong>Forward port</strong><span>Preview localhost from this host.</span></span></div>
                <div class="action-row"><span class="row-icon">⌕</span><span class="row-copy"><strong>Search transcript</strong><span>Find loaded messages.</span></span></div>
